{"tid":2216032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民陣見警商10.1遊行15分鐘極速完會 岑子杰批林鄭借疫情消滅反對聲音","createTime":"2020-09-24T11:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T11:32:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"525844e35a2871fce0fcc31b8fffbfa0c18374e1","tid":2216032,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"12名港青在中國被秘密羈押接近4星期，但兩地政府依然無視人民訴求，甚至封鎖被捕人消息。民陣昨日向警方申請不反對通知書，要求在10月1日舉辦大遊行，遊行主題定為「毋忘義士 釋放12」。民陣召集人岑子杰明言成功申請不反對通知書的機會渺茫，但為了12港人能盡快獲釋，並向政權表達香港人的關注，所有方法都要試。民陣今午在灣仔警署與警方商討「十一遊行」的安排，惟僅歷時15分鐘，岑子杰批港人已經8、9個月沒有遊行示威權利，形容「遊行權行已經放咗喺夾萬入面，個密碼鎖係壞，警方要求我哋撞正確密碼，先可以解鎖我哋嘅遊行權利，正正就係香港今日最可悲嘅狀態」。<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰在會後提到，今次會議是警方派過最少代表出席的一個，會議僅15分鐘就完結，警方向民陣提出很多「離譜」問題，包括民陣如何確保市民不會違反限聚令等。他指出，以往如能成功舉辦遊行，警方會在會上與他們傾談街站擺放等細節，惟是次會議沒有觸及，「自疫情以嚟，開會都未試過傾呢啲細節」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/5BE4PZGBMJCIHFLVUFCUUD5UPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2F5BE4PZGBMJCIHFLVUFCUUD5UPY%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheA%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=79fcf27c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2F5BE4PZGBMJCIHFLVUFCUUD5UPY%2F&h=285510e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/5BE4PZGBMJCIHFLVUFCUUD5UPY/</a>"},{"pid":"3084d113f1c389c80c4494fec08a6138ad5a94f0","tid":2216032,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d649f2335d3c1f6ef56581e97bab08a173316569","tid":2216032,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b274966cc9e1969e6da3080e04665b56b526533f","tid":2216032,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c7c84454072a36865a9a2ab64bf8c7292fd579","tid":2216032,"uid":297152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"柒婆賣港"},{"pid":"d929fb83c6b46ab693f409ea952b148bc680817f","tid":2216032,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:29:21.000Z","msg":"黑警戲都懶做"},{"pid":"7a4535a2793e54efcafcbb831c343d60792b11f2","tid":2216032,"uid":6435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d929fb83c6b46ab693f409ea952b148bc680817f","tid":2216032,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:29:21.000Z","msg":"黑警戲都懶做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"下次就會都唔開"}]}